#: ../../../release_details/9.4/annulus-implicit-widget.md:1
msgid "New vtkAnnulus Implicit Function and Widget"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/annulus-implicit-widget.md:3
msgid "Introduce implicit Annulus"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/annulus-implicit-widget.md:5
msgid ""
"The new `vtkAnnulus` implicit function represents an infinite annulus (two "
"co-axial cylinders). It exposes getters and setters for its axis, origin, "
"and inner/outer radii parameters. Changing those will automatically update "
"the base `vtkImplicitFunction`'s transform."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/annulus-implicit-widget.md:9
msgid "Add a new Implicit Annulus Widget"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/annulus-implicit-widget.md:11
msgid ""
"The new `vtkAnnulus` has a widget representation. The representation can be "
"manipulated through widget controls:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/annulus-implicit-widget.md:13
msgid "Rotate through the axis handle"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/annulus-implicit-widget.md:14
msgid "Translate through the center handle"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/annulus-implicit-widget.md:15
msgid "Scale through the outline handle"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/annulus-implicit-widget.md:16
msgid "Adjust inner/outer radii through the cone edges handles"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/annulus-implicit-widget.md:18
msgid ""
"Its underlying annulus can be used in any filter relying on implicit "
"functions (i.e. Clip, Slice)."
msgstr ""
